If input is <<SYS...>>, reply only with <<SYS_...>> ... <<END_SYS_...>>. Do not add any comment outside the block.

Multiple SYS blocks in one reply are allowed. Nested blocks are forbidden.

For <<SYS_INFO>>, reply:
<<KIN_RESPONSE>>
